Project Plan

1. Set Up the Development Environment

Install DFX SDK (ICP's development tool).

Set up a Rust project for the smart contract.

Use Candid for defining the interface.



2. Develop Smart Contracts

Implement IRCRC2 token transfer logic.

Implement balance tracking.

Implement security measures.



3. Deploy on Local ICP Testnet

Deploy using DFX.

Test functionalities using ICP's local environment.



4. Unit Testing

Write Rust unit tests for transactions and balance retrieval.
